markets.title: Will the **US-China competition** bill pass?
markets.rules_primary: If H.R. 4521 (referred as the America COMPETES Act, or the Bipartisan Innovation Act) or S.1260 (United States Innovation and Competition Act) have become law by November 8, 2022, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
See USICA in the Rulebook for more details.

One of the two bills must pass according to Congress.gov. If some, or all, of the contents of the bills are transferred into another bill (such as a reconciliation bill), and that bill becomes law, the market nonetheless resolves to No.
